body_html: Reconstructing the full FFT from the RFFT coefficients in Eigen is proving to be a bit tricky. The current PR implements the complex FFT, IFFT and the real FFT. The real IFFT is not implemented. I imagine someone with better Eigen knowledge than me would be better suited to implement it.
